{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://terraform.io/\">Terraform</a> est un logiciel open-source pour construire, modifier et versionner une infrastructure de manière sûre et efficace.</p><p>C&#x27;est un outil infrastructure as code.</p><p>Vous utilisez des fichiers de configuration au format .tf (HashiCorp) pour décrire les composants que vous souhaitez avoir dans votre infrastructure et Terraform s&#x27;occupe de générer un plan d&#x27;exécution et de l&#x27;exécuter.</p><p>Terraform supporte beaucoup de <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/search/providers\">fournisseurs d&#x27;infrastructure cloud</a> :</p><ul>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/scaleway/scaleway/latest/docs\">Scaleway</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/ovh/ovh/latest/docs\">OVH</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs\">AWS</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/terraform-provider-openstack/openstack/latest/docs\">OpenStack</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/azurerm/latest/docs\">Azure</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/google/latest/docs\">GCP</a></li>\n<li>ect...</li>\n</ul><h2>Installation</h2><p>Pour installer Terraform, rendez-vous sur <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://terraform.io/downloads.html\">la page de téléchargement</a>.</p><p>Téléchargez et installez le fichier adapté à votre système d&#x27;exploitation (Linux, Mac ou Windows).</p><p>Sur Arch Linux :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo pacman -S terraform\n</code></pre></div><h2>Utilisation</h2><p>Initialiser Terraform :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform init\n</code></pre></div><p>Vérifier la configuration :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform plan\n</code></pre></div><p>Mettre à jour l&#x27;infrastructure :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform apply\n</code></pre></div><p>Importer un objet existant :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform import openstack_lb_loadbalancer_v2.lb_1 &lt;ID&gt;\n</code></pre></div><p>Voir l&#x27;état actuel de l&#x27;infrastructure :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform show\n</code></pre></div><p>Gérer un workspace :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform workspace new &lt;name&gt; # Créer un workspace (ex: dev, prod)\nterraform workspace select &lt;name&gt; # Sélectionner un workspace\nterraform workspace delete &lt;name&gt; # Supprimer un workspace\nterraform workspace list # Lister les workspaces\n</code></pre></div><p>Linter les fichiers .tf :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform fmt -check -recursive\n</code></pre></div><p>Détruire une infrastructure :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">terraform destroy\n</code></pre></div><hr/><p>Références :</p><ul>\n<li>https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install</li>\n</ul></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Terraform.md","fileName":"Terraform","title":"Terraform","comments":true,"permalink":"terraform","datePublished":"2021-05-17T17:32","dateUpdated":"2021-05-17T17:32","publish":true,"rss":true},"__N_SSG":true}